<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#06080d">
<title>ASTRA — Autonomous Scientific Discovery</title>
<meta name="description" content="ASTRA: Autonomous System for Scientific Discovery in Astrophysics. Real-time AGI mission control dashboard.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@3.9.1/dist/chart.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/d3@7.8.5/dist/d3.min.js"></script>
<style>
/* ============================================================
   CSS RESET & ROOT VARIABLES
   ============================================================ */
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

:root {
  /* Color Palette */
  --bg-deep: #06080d;
  --bg-panel: rgba(10, 14, 24, 0.72);
  --bg-panel-hover: rgba(14, 20, 36, 0.85);
  --border-glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  --border-glow: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.25);

  --cyan: #00e5ff;
  --amber: #ffab00;
  --violet: #7c4dff;
  --emerald: #00e676;
  --coral: #ff5252;
  --blue: #7c4dff;

  --cyan-dim: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.15);
  --amber-dim: rgba(255, 171, 0, 0.15);
  --violet-dim: rgba(124, 77, 255, 0.15);
  --emerald-dim: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.15);
  --coral-dim: rgba(255, 82, 82, 0.15);

  --text-primary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1.0);
  --text-secondary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  --text-tertiary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);

  /* Typography */
  --font-heading: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  --font-mono: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;

  /* Spacing */
  --gap: 12px;
  --radius: 14px;
  --radius-sm: 8px;
}

/* ============================================================
   BASE STYLES
   ============================================================ */
html { font-size: 14px; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  min-height: 100vh;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  position: relative;
}

/* Particle canvas background */
#particle-canvas {
  position: fixed; inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Scanline overlay */
body::after {
  content: '';
  position: fixed; inset: 0;
  z-index: 9998;
  pointer-events: none;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(
    0deg,
    transparent,
    transparent 2px,
    rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03) 2px,
    rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03) 4px
  );
}

/* ============================================================
   KEYFRAME ANIMATIONS
   ============================================================ */
@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes slideUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50%      { opacity: 0.4; }
}
@keyframes glow {
  0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,229,255,0.3); }
  50%      { box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(0,229,255,0.6); }
}
@keyframes glowText {
  0%, 100% { text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,229,255,0.4); }
  50%      { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,229,255,0.8), 0 0 40px rgba(0,229,255,0.3); }
}
@keyframes borderGlow {
  0%, 100% { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.15); }
  50%      { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.45); }
}
@keyframes spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}
@keyframes typing {
  from { width: 0; }
  to   { width: 100%; }
}
@keyframes blink {
  50% { opacity: 0; }
}
@keyframes signalPulse {
  0%   { r: 3; opacity: 1; }
  100% { r: 14; opacity: 0; }
}
@keyframes arcFill {
  from { stroke-dashoffset: 283; }
}
@keyframes numberPop {
  0%   { transform: scale(1); }
  50%  { transform: scale(1.12); }
  100% { transform: scale(1); }
}
@keyframes scanline {
  0%   { transform: translateY(-100%); }
  100% { transform: translateY(100vh); }
}
@keyframes gradientShift {
  0%   { background-position: 0% 50%; }
  50%  { background-position: 100% 50%; }
  100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
}

/* ============================================================
   INLINE-STYLE EXTRACTION — Utility Classes (si- prefix)
   ============================================================ */
/* --- Dot color variants for panel titles --- */
.dot-cyan    { background: var(--cyan); }
.dot-amber   { background: var(--amber); }
.dot-violet  { background: var(--violet); }
.dot-emerald { background: var(--emerald); }
.dot-coral   { background: var(--coral); }
.dot-muted   { background: var(--text-tertiary); }

/* --- Fade-in animation delays (only on active tab) --- */
.tab-content.active .si-fade-in      { animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease both; }
.tab-content.active .si-fade-in-d1   { animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease 0.1s both; }
.tab-content.active .si-fade-in-d15  { animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease 0.15s both; }
.tab-content.active .si-fade-in-d2   { animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease 0.2s both; }
.tab-content.active .si-fade-in-d25  { animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease 0.25s both; }
.si-fade-in, .si-fade-in-d1, .si-fade-in-d15, .si-fade-in-d2, .si-fade-in-d25 {
  opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);
}

/* --- Card cells (Phase4 stat cells, arbiter, safety case) --- */
.si-stat-cell {
  background: var(--bg-panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 10px;
  text-align: center;
}
.si-stat-cell-sm {
  background: var(--bg-panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 8px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* --- Mono label: small uppercase mono label --- */
.si-mono-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
}
.si-mono-label-sm {
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.si-mono-label-xs {
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
}

/* --- Mono value readout --- */
.si-mono-value {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 1rem;
}
.si-mono-value-lg {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}
.si-mono-value-sm {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
}

/* --- Color accents --- */
.si-c-cyan     { color: var(--cyan); }
.si-c-amber    { color: var(--amber); }
.si-c-violet   { color: var(--violet); }
.si-c-emerald  { color: var(--emerald); }
.si-c-coral    { color: var(--coral); }
.si-c-muted    { color: var(--text-tertiary); }
.si-c-secondary { color: var(--text-secondary); }

/* --- Small muted text with margin-top --- */
.si-muted-note {
  margin-top: 10px;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
}

/* --- Info sub-label (Phase4 supervisor, ceremony sections) --- */
.si-info-label {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.si-info-sub {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.si-info-sub-lg {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  margin-top: 8px;
}

/* --- Rollback procedure label --- */
.si-rollback-label {
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.si-rollback-time {
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
}

/* --- Discovery panel full-width accent --- */
.si-discovery-full-cyan   { grid-column: 1 / -1; border-left: 3px solid var(--cyan); }
.si-discovery-full-amber  { grid-column: 1 / -1; border-left: 3px solid var(--amber); }
.si-discovery-accent-amber  { border-left: 3px solid var(--amber); }
.si-discovery-accent-coral  { border-left: 3px solid var(--coral); }
.si-discovery-accent-violet { border-left: 3px solid var(--violet); }
.si-discovery-accent-emerald { border-left: 3px solid var(--emerald); }

/* --- Canvas chart sizing --- */
.si-chart-canvas { width: 100%; height: 180px; }

/* --- Badge pill (anomaly count, pending count, health pct) --- */
.si-badge-amber {
  background: rgba(255,171,0,0.2);
  color: var(--amber);
  padding: 1px 8px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  margin-left: 8px;
}
.si-badge-emerald {
  background: rgba(0,230,118,0.2);
  color: var(--emerald);
  padding: 1px 8px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  margin-left: 8px;
}

/* --- Scroll container --- */
.si-scroll-sm {
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  max-height: 120px;
  overflow-y: auto;
}
.si-scroll-md {
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  max-height: 140px;
  overflow-y: auto;
}

/* --- Misc layout --- */
.si-p12  { padding: 12px; }
.si-p16  { padding: 16px; }
.si-hidden { display: none; }

/* --- Methodology footer --- */
.si-methodology-box {
  margin-top: 16px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  background: var(--bg-panel);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/* --- Phase 8.2: Extracted inline styles --- */
.text-center { text-align: center; }
.text-left { text-align: left; }
.color-cyan { color: var(--cyan); }
.color-amber { color: var(--amber); }
.color-violet { color: var(--violet); }
.color-emerald { color: var(--emerald); }
.color-coral { color: var(--coral); }
.color-blue { color: var(--blue); }
.color-text-secondary { color: var(--text-secondary); }
.color-text-tertiary { color: var(--text-tertiary); }

/* Discovery detail boxes by color */
.discovery-box-cyan    { color: var(--cyan); background: rgba(0,229,255,0.06); }
.discovery-box-amber   { color: var(--amber); background: rgba(255,171,0,0.06); }
.discovery-box-coral   { color: var(--coral); background: rgba(255,82,82,0.06); font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 10px 14px; }
.discovery-box-violet  { color: var(--violet); background: rgba(124,77,255,0.06); }
.discovery-box-emerald { color: var(--emerald); background: rgba(0,230,118,0.06); }

/* Improvement stat card backgrounds */
.si-stat-bg-amber   { background: rgba(255,171,0,0.06); }
.si-stat-bg-cyan    { background: rgba(0,229,255,0.06); }
.si-stat-bg-emerald { background: rgba(0,230,118,0.06); }
.si-stat-bg-violet  { background: rgba(124,77,255,0.06); }

/* Self-improve feedback summary */
.si-feedback-summary {
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--amber);
  margin-bottom: 12px; background: rgba(255,171,0,0.04); padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: 8px; line-height: 1.8;
}

/* Phase 4: info label (small uppercase tertiary) */
.si-info-label-upper {
  font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-bottom: 6px; text-transform: uppercase;
}
/* Phase 4: info values with mono font */
.si-info-mono-amber  { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--amber); }
.si-info-mono-violet { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--violet); }
.si-info-mono-secondary { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

/* ORP display */
.orp-gonogo { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--amber); }
.orp-checklist-info { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); }

/* Layout helpers */
.layout-flex-between { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 4px 0; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); }
.layout-flex-wrap { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.layout-flex-center-gap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.layout-flex-gap8 { margin-top: 12px; display: flex; gap: 8px; }
.layout-align-left { min-width: 160px; }
.layout-flex1 { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; }
.health-components-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill,minmax(200px,1fr)); gap: 10px; }

/* Spacing helpers */
.mt-4  { margin-top: 4px; }
.mt-8  { margin-top: 8px; }
.mt-12 { margin-top: 12px; }
.mb-6  { margin-bottom: 6px; }
.mb-10 { margin-bottom: 10px; }
.mb-12 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
.m-8-0-4 { margin: 8px 0 4px; }
.pt-8-bt { padding-top: 8px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass); }
.p4-claims-gap { gap: 12px; padding: 12px; }

/* Discovery data table */
.discovery-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
.discovery-table-header { color: var(--text-tertiary); }

/* Trend label badge */
.si-trend-badge { margin-left: 12px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; }
.si-method-td-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); }

/* Scrollable panel body */
.panel-body-sm { padding: 12px 16px; }
.panel-body-scroll { padding: 12px 16px; overflow-x: auto; }
.panel-body-md { padding: 14px 16px; }
.panel-body-lg { padding: 16px 20px; }

/* Header pipe separator */
.header-sep { color: var(--text-tertiary); }

/* --- Phase 8.3: Exploration Coverage Matrix --- */
.si-coverage-canvas-wrap {
  width: 100%; height: 260px; position: relative;
}
.si-coverage-canvas-wrap canvas {
  width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important;
}
.si-key-metrics-bar {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
  gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.si-key-metric {
  background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 10px 14px; text-align: center;
}
.si-key-metric-val {
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cyan);
}
.si-key-metric-label {
  font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.55rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 4px;
}
.si-key-metric-delta {
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; margin-top: 2px;
}

/* Reduced motion */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}

/* ============================================================
   GLASS PANEL BASE
   ============================================================ */
.panel {
  background: var(--bg-panel);
  backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 16px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  transition: border-color 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
}
.panel:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-glow);
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,229,255,0.06), inset 0 0 30px rgba(0,229,255,0.02);
}
.panel::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--cyan), transparent);
  opacity: 0.3;
}
.panel-decision-engine::before {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--violet), transparent);
}
.panel-charts::before {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--amber), transparent);
}
.panel-decisions::before {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--emerald), transparent);
}

.panel-title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-top: 0;
  letter-spacing: 2.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.panel-title .dot {
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--cyan);
  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

/* ============================================================
   HEADER — COMPACT STATUS BAR
   ============================================================ */
.header {
  position: sticky; top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 6px 16px;
  background: rgba(6, 8, 13, 0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  background-clip: padding-box;
}
.header::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--violet), var(--cyan), var(--amber), var(--cyan), var(--violet));
  background-size: 300% 100%;
  animation: gradientShift 6s ease infinite;
}

.header-left {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.logo-mark {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--violet));
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  animation: glowText 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  cursor: default;
}
.logo-sub {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.header-center {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--emerald);
}
.status-dot {
  width: 8px; height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--emerald);
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--emerald);
  animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.header-right {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
}
.header-right .version {
  background: var(--cyan-dim);
  color: var(--cyan);
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* ============================================================
   MAIN LAYOUT — CSS GRID
   ============================================================ */
.dashboard {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  padding: var(--gap);
  max-width: 1800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.main-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr 1fr;
  grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
  grid-template-areas:
    "left-top    brain     right-top"
    "left-bottom brain     right-bottom";
  gap: var(--gap);
  height: calc(100vh - 120px);
}

.panel-activity   { grid-area: left-top; animation-delay: 0.1s; }
.panel-decision-engine { grid-area: left-bottom; animation-delay: 0.15s; }
.panel-brain      { grid-area: brain; animation-delay: 0.05s; }
.panel-charts     { grid-area: right-top; animation-delay: 0.2s; }
.panel-decisions  { grid-area: right-bottom; animation-delay: 0.25s; }

/* Metrics full-width row */
.metrics-row {
  margin-top: var(--gap);
  animation: slideUp 0.7s ease-out 0.3s both;
}

/* Gauge floats inside brain panel */
.gauge-container {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 16px; right: 16px;
  z-index: 5;
}

/* ============================================================
   TABLET LAYOUT
   ============================================================ */
@media (max-width: 1199px) and (min-width: 768px) {
  .main-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: minmax(320px, 400px) minmax(250px, 340px) minmax(250px, 340px);
    grid-template-areas:
      "brain       brain"
      "left-top    right-top"
      "left-bottom right-bottom";
    height: auto;
  }
  .panel-brain { min-height: 320px; }
  .panel-charts { max-height: 340px; }
  .panel-activity { max-height: 340px; }
  .panel-decisions { max-height: 340px; }
  .panel-decision-engine { max-height: 340px; }
}

/* ============================================================
   MOBILE LAYOUT
   ============================================================ */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  html { font-size: 15px; }
  .main-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: minmax(300px, 350px) auto auto auto auto;
    grid-template-areas:
      "brain"
      "left-top"
      "left-bottom"
      "right-top"
      "right-bottom";
    height: auto;
  }
  .header { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; padding: 8px 12px; }
  .header-center { order: 3; width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
  .header-center span { font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .header-right span { font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .logo-sub { font-size: 0.75rem; }
  .panel-brain { min-height: 300px; max-height: 350px; }
  .gauge-container { bottom: 8px; right: 8px; }
  .gauge-container svg { width: 90px; height: 90px; }
  .panel-charts { max-height: none; overflow: visible; }
  .charts-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: repeat(3, minmax(70px, 1fr));
  }
  .activity-feed { font-size: 0.78rem; }
  .mini-chart-title { font-size: 0.7rem; }
  .metric-label { font-size: 0.65rem; }
  .decision-badge { font-size: 0.65rem; }
  .footer a {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 8px;
    min-height: 44px;
    line-height: 20px;
  }
}

/* ============================================================
   PANEL 1 — AGI BRAIN VISUALIZATION
   ============================================================ */
.panel-brain {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  position: relative;
  min-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.panel-brain .panel-title { position: relative; z-index: 3; }
#brain-svg {
  flex: 1;
  width: 100%;
  min-height: 0;
}
#brain-svg text {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* ============================================================
   PANEL 2 — ACTIVITY STREAM
   ============================================================ */
.panel-activity {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  min-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.activity-feed {
  flex: 1;
  overflow-y: auto;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 0%, black 12%, black 100%);
  -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 0%, black 12%, black 100%);
  padding-right: 4px;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}
.activity-feed::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 3px; }
.activity-feed::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
.activity-feed::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(0,229,255,0.2); border-radius: 2px; }

.activity-line {
  padding: 3px 0;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-out forwards;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
}
.activity-line .ts {
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
}
.activity-line .module {
  font-weight: 700;
}
.activity-line.type-reading .module  { color: var(--blue); }
.activity-line.type-scoring .module  { color: var(--cyan); }
.activity-line.type-writing .module  { color: var(--emerald); }
.activity-line.type-running .module  { color: var(--amber); }
.activity-line.type-evaluating .module { color: var(--violet); }
.activity-line.type-updating .module { color: var(--amber); }

/* ============================================================
   PANEL 3 — DECISION ENGINE / OODA-STYLE CYCLE
   ============================================================ */
.panel-decision-engine {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  min-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.cycle-phases {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
  flex: 1;
}
.phase-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px 12px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.5s ease;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.phase-item.active {
  border-color: var(--cyan);
  background: var(--cyan-dim);
  animation: borderGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.phase-item .phase-icon {
  width: 32px; height: 32px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-weight: 700;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  border: 2px solid var(--text-tertiary);
  transition: all 0.5s ease;
}
.phase-item.active .phase-icon {
  border-color: var(--cyan);
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,229,255,0.4);
  color: var(--cyan);
}
.phase-info {
  flex: 1;
}
.phase-name {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  transition: color 0.5s;
}
.phase-item.active .phase-name { color: var(--cyan); }
.phase-desc {
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  margin-top: 2px;
  transition: color 0.5s;
}
.phase-item.active .phase-desc { color: var(--text-secondary); }
.phase-progress {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0; left: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--cyan);
  border-radius: 1px;
  width: 0;
  transition: width 5s linear;
}
.phase-item.active .phase-progress {
  width: 100%;
}
/* Connecting lines between phases */
.phase-connector {
  width: 2px; height: 10px;
  margin-left: 26px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--text-tertiary), transparent);
  opacity: 0.3;
}

/* ============================================================
   PANEL 4 — MINI CHARTS GRID
   ============================================================ */
.panel-charts {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  min-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.charts-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 8px;
  flex: 1;
  min-height: 0;
}
.mini-chart {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 8px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
  min-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.mini-chart:hover { border-color: var(--border-glow); }
.mini-chart-title {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.mini-chart canvas {
  flex: 1;
  min-height: 0;
}

/* ============================================================
   PANEL 5 — METRICS BAR
   ============================================================ */
.metrics-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(135px, 1fr));
  gap: 8px;
}
.metric-box {
  background: var(--bg-panel);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 12px 14px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 4px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: default;
}
.metric-box:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-glow);
  background: var(--bg-panel-hover);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 0 12px rgba(0,229,255,0.08);
}
.metric-box::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--cyan), transparent);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.3s;
}
.metric-box:hover::before { opacity: 0.5; }

.metric-value {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  line-height: 1;
}
.metric-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.metric-sparkline {
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.metric-sparkline polyline {
  fill: none;
  stroke: var(--cyan);
  stroke-width: 1.5;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-linejoin: round;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* ============================================================
   PANEL 6 — AUTONOMOUS DECISION LOG
   ============================================================ */
.panel-decisions {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  min-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.decisions-list {
  flex: 1;
  overflow-y: auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
}
.decisions-list::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 3px; }
.decisions-list::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(0,229,255,0.2); border-radius: 2px; }

.decision-entry {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out both;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
}
.decision-entry:hover { border-color: var(--border-glow); }

.decision-icon {
  width: 28px; height: 28px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.decision-icon.expand   { background: var(--cyan-dim);    color: var(--cyan); }
.decision-icon.prune    { background: var(--coral-dim);   color: var(--coral); }
.decision-icon.merge    { background: var(--violet-dim);  color: var(--violet); }
.decision-icon.escalate { background: var(--amber-dim);   color: var(--amber); }
.decision-icon.confirm  { background: var(--emerald-dim); color: var(--emerald); }

.decision-body { flex: 1; }
.decision-ts {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
}
.decision-text {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-top: 2px;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.decision-badge {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.55rem;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-top: 4px;
  display: inline-block;
}
.badge-success       { background: var(--emerald-dim); color: var(--emerald); }
.badge-pending       { background: var(--amber-dim);   color: var(--amber); }
.badge-investigating { background: var(--cyan-dim);    color: var(--cyan); }

/* ============================================================
   NEURAL CONFIDENCE GAUGE
   ============================================================ */
.gauge-svg {
  width: 120px;
  height: 120px;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(0,229,255,0.3));
}
.gauge-bg {
  fill: none;
  stroke: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  stroke-width: 8;
}
.gauge-fill {
  fill: none;
  stroke: url(#gaugeGradient);
  stroke-width: 8;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-dasharray: 283;
  stroke-dashoffset: 283;
  transform: rotate(-90deg);
  transform-origin: center;
  transition: stroke-dashoffset 1.5s ease-out;
}
.gauge-value {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  fill: var(--text-primary);
  text-anchor: middle;
  dominant-baseline: central;
}
.gauge-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.5rem;
  fill: var(--text-tertiary);
  text-anchor: middle;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.gauge-dot {
  fill: var(--cyan);
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px var(--cyan));
}

/* ============================================================
   FOOTER
   ============================================================ */
.footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 16px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
}
.footer a { color: var(--cyan); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding: 12px 8px; min-height: 44px; }
.footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

/* ============================================================
   SCROLLBAR GLOBAL
   ============================================================ */
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 5px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(0,229,255,0.15); border-radius: 3px; }

/* ============================================================
   AGI CONTROL ROOM — SAFETY STRIP
   ============================================================ */
.safety-strip {
  position: sticky; top: 38px; z-index: 100;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  padding: 8px 20px;
  background: rgba(10,12,18,0.95);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,82,82,0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem;
}
.safety-beacon {
  width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--emerald);
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--emerald);
  animation: beaconPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.safety-beacon.warning { background: var(--amber); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--amber); }
.safety-beacon.critical { background: var(--coral); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--coral); }
@keyframes beaconPulse { 0%,100% { opacity:1; } 50% { opacity:0.5; } }

.autonomy-phase {
  display: flex; gap: 2px; align-items: center; margin-left: 4px;
}
.phase-pip {
  padding: 2px 8px; font-size: 0.65rem; border-radius: 3px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: var(--text-tertiary);
  font-family: var(--font-mono); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.phase-pip.active {
  background: var(--cyan-dim); color: var(--cyan);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.3);
}

.safety-spacer { flex: 1; }

.safety-btn {
  padding: 8px 14px; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  min-height: 44px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
}
.safety-btn:active { transform: scale(0.96); }
.safety-btn.btn-pause {
  background: var(--amber); color: #000;
}
.safety-btn.btn-safe {
  background: var(--blue); color: #fff;
}
.safety-btn.btn-estop {
  background: var(--coral); color: #fff; min-width: 90px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255,82,82,0.4);
  font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 8px 18px;
}
.safety-btn.btn-estop:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,82,82,0.7); }
.safety-btn.btn-resume {
  background: var(--emerald); color: #000;
}
.safety-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.3; cursor: not-allowed; }

.sor-badge {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
  color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.7rem;
}
.sor-badge .sor-dot {
  width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--violet);
}

.engine-state-badge {
  padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
  background: rgba(0,230,118,0.15); color: var(--emerald);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,230,118,0.25);
}
.engine-state-badge.paused { background: rgba(255,171,0,0.15); color: var(--amber); border-color: rgba(255,171,0,0.25); }
.engine-state-badge.stopped { background: rgba(255,82,82,0.15); color: var(--coral); border-color: rgba(255,82,82,0.25); }
.engine-state-badge.safe-mode { background: rgba(124,77,255,0.15); color: var(--blue); border-color: rgba(124,77,255,0.25); }

/* ============================================================
   AGI CONTROL ROOM — TAB BAR
   ============================================================ */
.tab-bar {
  display: flex; gap: 0; padding: 0 20px;
  background: rgba(10,14,24,0.6);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  position: sticky; top: 74px; z-index: 99;
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  overflow-x: auto;
}
.tab-bar::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 3px; }
.tab-bar::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
.tab-bar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(0,229,255,0.2); border-radius: 2px; }
.tab-btn {
  padding: 12px 24px; border: none; background: transparent; cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--text-tertiary); text-transform: uppercase;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  min-height: 44px; min-width: 44px;
}
.tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text-secondary); }
.skip-link { position:absolute;top:-50px;left:0;background:var(--cyan);color:#000;padding:12px 16px;min-height:44px;box-sizing:border-box;z-index:9999;font-family:var(--font-mono);transition:top 0.2s;line-height:20px; }
.skip-link:focus { top:0; }
.tab-btn:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--cyan); outline-offset: 2px; border-radius: 4px; }
*:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--cyan); outline-offset: 2px; }
.tab-btn.active {
  color: var(--cyan); border-bottom-color: var(--cyan);
}
.tab-content { display: none; }
.tab-content.active { display: block; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .site-header, .command-header, header {
    position: static !important;
  }
  .safety-strip {
    position: static !important;
    top: auto !important;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 12px;
  }
  .autonomy-phase { display: none; }
  .sor-badge { display: none; }
  .tab-bar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0 !important;
    z-index: 1000;
    overflow-x: auto; padding: 0 8px;
  }
  .tab-btn { padding: 10px 8px; font-size: 0.55rem; white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .tab-label { display: none; }
  .tab-btn { padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 1rem; min-width: 40px; text-align: center; }
}
@media (max-width: 500px) {
  .persistence-card { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .persistence-stat .stat-value { font-size: 1.1rem; }
}
@media (max-width: 400px) {
  .main-grid, .safety-grid, .control-grid, .health-grid { gap: 8px; padding: 8px; }
  .panel-title { font-size: 0.65rem; }
}

/* Chart loading state */
.chart-loading { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--text-tertiary); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; min-height: 120px; }
.chart-loading::before { content: '⟳'; animation: spin 1s linear infinite; margin-right: 8px; display: inline-block; }
@keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

/* Verdict row utility classes */
.verdict-row { padding: 4px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass); }
.verdict-decision { font-weight: 600; }
.verdict-meta { color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-left: 6px; }
.verdict-cycle { color: var(--text-tertiary); float: right; }
.verdict-empty { color: var(--text-tertiary); }

/* Utility: background none */
.bg-none { background: none !important; }
.mb-16 { margin-bottom: 16px; }

/* ============================================================
   AGI CONTROL ROOM — SAFETY TAB PANELS
   ============================================================ */
.safety-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap);
  padding: var(--gap);
}
.safety-grid .panel-full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
@media (max-width: 900px) { .safety-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* State Space Navigator */
.state-space-svg { width: 100%; height: 320px; background: rgba(6,8,13,0.5); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }
.state-space-svg .trajectory { fill: none; stroke: var(--cyan); stroke-width: 2; opacity: 0.7; }
.state-space-svg .current-pos { fill: var(--cyan); }
.state-space-svg .basin-nominal { fill: rgba(0,230,118,0.05); stroke: var(--emerald); stroke-width: 1; stroke-dasharray: 4 2; }
.state-space-svg .basin-warning { fill: none; stroke: var(--amber); stroke-width: 1; stroke-dasharray: 6 3; }
.state-space-svg .basin-critical { fill: none; stroke: var(--coral); stroke-width: 1; stroke-dasharray: 3 3; }
.state-space-svg .axis-label { fill: var(--text-tertiary); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; }

/* Gauge bars */
.gauge-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.gauge-label-text { width: 140px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
.gauge-bar-bg { flex: 1; height: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
.gauge-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; transition: width 0.8s ease; }
.gauge-bar-fill.nominal { background: var(--emerald); }
.gauge-bar-fill.warning { background: var(--amber); }
.gauge-bar-fill.critical { background: var(--coral); }
.gauge-val { width: 50px; text-align: right; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
.gauge-status { width: 70px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
.gauge-status.nominal { color: var(--emerald); }
.gauge-status.warning { color: var(--amber); }
.gauge-status.critical { color: var(--coral); }

/* Alert stream */
.alert-stream { max-height: 160px; overflow-y: auto; }
.alert-item { display: flex; gap: 8px; padding: 4px 0; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
.alert-item .alert-sev { width: 16px; text-align: center; }
.alert-item .alert-time { color: var(--text-tertiary); width: 65px; }
.alert-item .alert-msg { color: var(--text-secondary); flex: 1; }

/* Alignment bars */
.align-score-big { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2.4rem; color: var(--cyan); }
.align-trend { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--emerald); margin-left: 8px; }
.align-dim { margin-bottom: 8px; }
.align-dim-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.align-dim-bar { height: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; }
.align-dim-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; transition: width 0.8s ease; }

/* ============================================================
   AGI CONTROL ROOM — CONTROL TAB
   ============================================================ */
.control-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap);
  padding: var(--gap);
}
.control-grid .panel-full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
@media (max-width: 900px) { .control-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.intervention-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.intervention-btn {
  padding: 14px 24px; border: none; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase; transition: all 0.15s; flex: 1; min-width: 140px; text-align: center;
}
.intervention-btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
.intervention-btn.btn-pause-big { background: rgba(255,171,0,0.2); color: var(--amber); border: 1px solid rgba(255,171,0,0.3); }
.intervention-btn.btn-pause-big:hover { background: rgba(255,171,0,0.3); }
.intervention-btn.btn-stop-big {
  background: rgba(255,82,82,0.2); color: var(--coral); border: 2px solid var(--coral);
  box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255,82,82,0.2);
}
.intervention-btn.btn-stop-big:hover { background: rgba(255,82,82,0.35); box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(255,82,82,0.4); }
.intervention-btn.btn-safe-big { background: rgba(124,77,255,0.2); color: var(--blue); border: 1px solid rgba(124,77,255,0.3); }
.intervention-btn.btn-resume-big { background: rgba(0,230,118,0.2); color: var(--emerald); border: 1px solid rgba(0,230,118,0.3); }

.quick-actions { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 12px; }
.quick-action-btn {
  padding: 10px 16px; border: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  background: var(--bg-panel); color: var(--text-secondary); cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.68rem; transition: all 0.15s;
  min-height: 44px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
}
.quick-action-btn:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--cyan); }

.approval-item {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 10px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  margin-bottom: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
}
.approval-info { flex: 1; }
.approval-name { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
.approval-meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 2px; }
.approval-actions { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
.approval-btn {
  width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.approval-btn.approve { background: rgba(0,230,118,0.2); color: var(--emerald); }
.approval-btn.approve:hover { background: rgba(0,230,118,0.4); }
.approval-btn.reject { background: rgba(255,82,82,0.2); color: var(--coral); }
.approval-btn.reject:hover { background: rgba(255,82,82,0.4); }

.sor-panel-name { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
.sor-panel-detail { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 4px; }
.sor-actions-log { margin-top: 12px; max-height: 160px; overflow-y: auto; }
.sor-action-item { padding: 4px 0; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--text-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }

/* ============================================================
   AGI CONTROL ROOM — HEALTH TAB
   ============================================================ */
.health-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--gap);
  padding: var(--gap);
}
.health-grid .panel-full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
@media (max-width: 900px) { .health-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .health-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

.component-card {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 12px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glass); border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
}
.component-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
.component-dot.ok { background: var(--emerald); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--emerald); }
.component-dot.degraded { background: var(--amber); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--amber); }
.component-dot.down { background: var(--coral); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--coral); }
.component-name { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
.component-metric { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 2px; }

.audit-log { max-height: 350px; overflow-y: auto; }
.audit-entry { display: flex; gap: 8px; padding: 5px 0; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.68rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
.audit-entry .audit-time { color: var(--text-tertiary); width: 70px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.audit-entry .audit-type { width: 60px; flex-shrink: 0; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; }
.audit-entry .audit-type.safety { color: var(--coral); }
.audit-entry .audit-type.discovery { color: var(--cyan); }
.audit-entry .audit-type.decision { color: var(--amber); }
.audit-entry .audit-type.system { color: var(--text-tertiary); }
.audit-entry .audit-msg { color: var(--text-secondary); flex: 1; }

.empty-state {
  text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px;
  color: var(--text-tertiary); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem;
}

/* ============================================================
   PHASE 7+10.1 — ADDITIONAL STYLES
   ============================================================ */

/* Panel header — extracted from inline styles */
.panel-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
}
.panel-header .panel-icon {
  font-size: 1rem;
}

/* Hypothesis Pipeline */
.hyp-pipeline { margin-bottom: 24px; }
.hyp-pipeline-header {
  font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: var(--cyan); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.hyp-pipeline-header::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), transparent); }
.hyp-phase-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.hyp-phase-label {
  font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 4px;
}
.hyp-phase-label.validated { color: var(--emerald); }
.hyp-phase-label.testing { color: var(--cyan); }
.hyp-phase-label.proposed { color: var(--amber); }
.hyp-phase-label.archived { color: var(--text-tertiary); }
.hyp-phase-label .hyp-count { opacity: 0.6; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; }
.hyp-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; }
.hyp-card {
  background: rgba(15,20,35,0.5); border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 14px; backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.hyp-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.3); }
.hyp-card-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.hyp-card-id { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); }
.hyp-card-domain {
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 3px; background: rgba(0,229,255,0.1); color: var(--cyan);
}
.hyp-card-name { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.3; }
.hyp-card-conf { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.hyp-conf-bar { flex: 1; height: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; }
.hyp-conf-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; transition: width 0.3s; }
.hyp-conf-fill.high { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--emerald), #4aedc4); }
.hyp-conf-fill.mid { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), #4dc9f6); }
.hyp-conf-fill.low { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--amber), #ffd54f); }
.hyp-conf-fill.vlow { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--coral), #ff8a80); }
.hyp-conf-val { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-secondary); min-width: 36px; text-align: right; }
.hyp-card-desc { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.35; }
.hyp-card.archived-card { opacity: 0.5; }
.hyp-card.archived-card:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

/* Discoveries grid — mobile single column */
.discoveries-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 8px 0;
}
.discoveries-grid .panel-full-width {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .discoveries-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
  }
}

/* Rollback procedures — 2x2 on mobile */
.rollback-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 12px;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .rollback-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
}

/* Persistence metric card */
.persistence-card {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
  gap: 10px;
}
.persistence-stat {
  background: rgba(124, 77, 255, 0.06);
  padding: 12px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-align: center;
}
.persistence-stat .stat-value {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  color: var(--violet);
}
.persistence-stat .stat-label {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.component-card, .persistence-stat {
  transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}
.component-card:hover, .persistence-stat:hover {
  background: rgba(124, 77, 255, 0.12);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

/* Discovery stat badge */
.discovery-stat-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.badge-fdr {
  background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.1);
  color: var(--cyan);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.2);
}
.badge-effect {
  background: rgba(255, 171, 0, 0.1);
  color: var(--amber);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 171, 0, 0.2);
}

/* Self-improvement grid — responsive */
.improvement-stats-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.improvement-stat-card {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  padding: 14px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-align: center;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .improvement-stats-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
}

/* Discovery detail box */
.discovery-detail-box {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

/* Discovery meta row */
.discovery-meta {
  margin-top: 10px;
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 16px;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  overflow-wrap: break-word;
  word-break: break-word;
}

/* Discovery description text */
.discovery-desc {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Discovery panel body padding */
.discovery-body { padding: 16px 20px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; }

/* Phase 4 responsive grids (replaces inline styles) */
.phase4-safety-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 8px;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .phase4-safety-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
  }
}
.phase4-claims-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 8px;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .phase4-claims-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
  }
}

/* ============================================================
   LITERATURE TAB STYLES
   ============================================================ */
.lit-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 8px 0;
}
.lit-grid .panel-full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .lit-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
}
/* --- Stigmergy tab --- */
.stig-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 8px 0;
}
.stig-grid .panel-full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .stig-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
}
.stig-agent-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }
.stig-agent-card {
  background: rgba(0,229,255,0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.12);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 14px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}
.stig-agent-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.3); }
.stig-agent-name { font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--cyan); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.stig-agent-role { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.stig-agent-stat { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-secondary); padding: 2px 0; }
.stig-agent-stat span:last-child { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; }
.stig-status-dot { display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle; }
.stig-status-dot.active { background: var(--emerald); box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--emerald); }
.stig-status-dot.idle { background: var(--amber); }
.stig-status-dot.offline { background: var(--text-tertiary); }
.stig-gap-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin: 4px 0; }
.stig-gap-bar .bar-bg { flex: 1; height: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
.stig-gap-bar .bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; transition: width 0.4s ease; }
.stig-gap-bar .bar-label { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); min-width: 100px; }
.stig-gap-bar .bar-value { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-secondary); min-width: 36px; text-align: right; }
.stig-ab-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
.stig-ab-table th { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); text-align: left; padding: 6px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.stig-ab-table td { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-secondary); padding: 6px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; }
.stig-ab-winner { color: var(--emerald); font-weight: 600; }
.stig-gordon-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
.stig-gordon-table th { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); text-align: left; padding: 6px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.stig-gordon-table td { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-secondary); padding: 6px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
.stig-gordon-table td:nth-child(2) { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; }
.lit-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
.lit-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
}
.lit-table th {
  text-align: left;
  padding: 8px 10px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}
.lit-table td {
  padding: 7px 10px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
}
.lit-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(0,229,255,0.03); }
.lit-title-cell { max-width: 280px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85) !important; }
.lit-authors-cell { max-width: 160px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
.lit-arxiv-cell { font-size: 10px; color: var(--cyan) !important; opacity: 0.7; }
.lit-score-cell { min-width: 120px; }
.lit-score-bar {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 60px;
  height: 6px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: 3px;
  overflow: hidden;
  vertical-align: middle;
  margin-right: 6px;
}
.lit-score-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; transition: width 0.6s ease; }
.lit-score-cell span { font-size: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
.lit-citation-container { overflow: hidden; border-radius: 8px; }
.lit-bar-container { padding: 8px; }
.lit-metrics-cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 8px;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .lit-metrics-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
}
.lit-metric-card {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 16px 8px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 8px;
}
.lit-metric-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.lit-metric-value { font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.lit-metric-label { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing: 1px; }
.lit-empty-state {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 20px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12px;
}

/* ============================================================
   SELF-IMPROVEMENT TAB STYLES
   ============================================================ */
.si-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 8px 0;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .si-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
}
.si-chart-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 280px;
}
.si-chart-container canvas {
  width: 100% !important;
  height: 100% !important;
}
.si-method-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
}
.si-method-table thead th {
  text-align: left;
  padding: 8px 10px;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.si-method-table tbody td {
  padding: 7px 10px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
}
.si-method-table tbody tr:hover {
  background: rgba(0,229,255,0.04);
}
.si-rate-good { color: var(--emerald); }
.si-rate-mid  { color: var(--amber); }
.si-rate-bad  { color: var(--coral); }
.si-affinity-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 5px 0;
}
.si-affinity-label {
  min-width: 130px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  text-align: right;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.si-affinity-track {
  flex: 1;
  height: 18px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
}
.si-affinity-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), rgba(0,229,255,0.4));
  transition: width 0.8s ease-out;
}
.si-affinity-value {
  min-width: 50px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--cyan);
}
.si-metrics-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .si-metrics-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
}
.si-metric-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 16px 14px;
  text-align: center;
}
.si-metric-label {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 0.55rem;
  letter-spacing: 1.2px;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.si-metric-value {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.si-metric-sub {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.si-metric-sub span {
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
}
.si-delta-pos { color: var(--emerald) !important; }
.si-delta-neg { color: var(--coral) !important; }
.si-delta-flat { color: var(--text-tertiary) !important; }
</style>
<noscript><style>.tab-content,.header,.tab-bar{display:none}</style></noscript>
</head>
<body>
<noscript><div style="color:#00e5ff;font-family:monospace;text-align:center;padding:40px">ASTRA Dashboard requires JavaScript to render real-time data visualizations.</div></noscript>
<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>

<!-- ============================================================
     PARTICLE BACKGROUND CANVAS
     ============================================================ -->
<canvas id="particle-canvas" aria-label="Animated particle background"></canvas>

<!-- ============================================================
     HEADER — COMPACT STATUS BAR
     ============================================================ -->
<header class="header">
  <div class="header-left">
    <div>
      <h1 class="logo-mark" style="margin:0;font-size:inherit">ASTRA</h1>
      <div class="logo-sub">Autonomous Scientific Discovery</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="header-center">
    <span class="status-dot"></span>
    <span>AUTONOMOUS MODE&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp;&nbsp;ACTIVE</span>
  </div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <span id="utc-clock" aria-live="off" aria-label="UTC clock">--:--:--</span>
    <span class="header-sep">|</span>
    <span>UP <span id="uptime" aria-live="polite" aria-label="System uptime">0d 0h 0m</span></span>
    <span class="version">v4.7</span>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ============================================================
     AGI CONTROL ROOM — SAFETY STRIP (ALWAYS VISIBLE)
     ============================================================ -->
<div class="safety-strip" id="safety-strip">
  <div class="safety-beacon" id="safety-beacon" title="System Status" aria-live="polite" aria-label="System safety status"></div>
  <span class="engine-state-badge" id="engine-state-badge" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Engine state">NOMINAL</span>
  <div class="autonomy-phase">
    <span class="phase-pip active" id="phase-shadow">SHADOW</span>
    <span class="phase-pip" id="phase-supervised">SUPERVISED</span>
    <span class="phase-pip" id="phase-conditional">CONDITIONAL</span>
    <span class="phase-pip" id="phase-full">FULL</span>
  </div>
  <div class="safety-spacer"></div>
  <div class="sor-badge">
    <span class="sor-dot"></span>
    <span id="sor-strip-name">Supervisor: Not Set</span>
  </div>
  <button class="safety-btn btn-pause" id="btn-strip-pause" onclick="safetyAction('pause')" title="Pause Discovery Engine" aria-label="Pause discovery engine">⏸ PAUSE</button>
  <button class="safety-btn btn-safe" id="btn-strip-safe" onclick="safetyAction('safe-mode')" title="Switch to Safe Mode" aria-label="Switch to safe mode">🛡 SAFE</button>
  <button class="safety-btn btn-resume" id="btn-strip-resume" onclick="safetyAction('resume')" title="Resume Engine" aria-label="Resume engine" style="display:none">▶ RESUME</button>
  <button class="safety-btn btn-estop" id="btn-strip-estop" onclick="confirmEstop()" title="Emergency Stop" aria-label="Emergency stop">🛑 E-STOP</button>
</div>

<!-- ============================================================
     AGI CONTROL ROOM — TAB BAR
     ============================================================ -->
<nav class="tab-bar" role="tablist" aria-label="Dashboard navigation">
  <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="overview" role="tab" id="tab-btn-overview" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tab-overview" onclick="switchTab('overview')" aria-label="Overview tab">◉ <span class="tab-label">OVERVIEW</span></button>
  <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="safety" role="tab" id="tab-btn-safety" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tab-safety" onclick="switchTab('safety')" aria-label="Safety monitoring tab">◈ <span class="tab-label">SAFETY</span></button>
  <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="control" role="tab" id="tab-btn-control" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tab-control" onclick="switchTab('control')" aria-label="Engine control tab">⚙ <span class="tab-label">CONTROL</span></button>
  <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="health" role="tab" id="tab-btn-health" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tab-health" onclick="switchTab('health')" aria-label="System health tab">♥ <span class="tab-label">HEALTH</span></button>
  <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="phase4" role="tab" id="tab-btn-phase4" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tab-phase4" onclick="switchTab('phase4')" aria-label="Phase 4 operational readiness tab">⬡ <span class="tab-label">PHASE 4</span></button>
  <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="discoveries" role="tab" id="tab-btn-discoveries" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tab-discoveries" onclick="switchTab('discoveries')" aria-label="Scientific discoveries tab">✦ <span class="tab-label">DISCOVERIES</span></button>
  <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="selfimprove" role="tab" id="tab-btn-selfimprove" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tab-selfimprove" onclick="switchTab('selfimprove')" aria-label="Self-improvement metrics tab">⟳ <span class="tab-label">SELF-IMPROVE</span></button>
  <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="literature" role="tab" id="tab-btn-literature" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tab-literature" onclick="switchTab('literature')" aria-label="Literature and citations tab">📚 <span class="tab-label">LITERATURE</span></button>
  <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="stigmergy" role="tab" id="tab-btn-stigmergy" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tab-stigmergy" onclick="switchTab('stigmergy')" aria-label="Stigmergy swarm intelligence tab">🐜 <span class="tab-label">STIGMERGY</span></button>
</nav>

<!-- ============================================================
     MAIN DASHBOARD
     ============================================================ -->
<main class="dashboard" role="main" id="main-content">

<!-- ==================== TAB: OVERVIEW (existing) ==================== -->
<div class="tab-content active" id="tab-overview" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-btn-overview">

  <!-- ========== MAIN GRID ========== -->
  <div class="main-grid">

    <!-- ==============================
         LEFT TOP: ACTIVITY STREAM
         ============================== -->
    <div class="panel panel-activity">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot"></span>ACTIVITY STREAM</h2>
      <div class="activity-feed" id="activity-feed" role="log" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Activity stream"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==============================
         LEFT BOTTOM: DECISION ENGINE
         ============================== -->
    <div class="panel panel-decision-engine">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-violet"></span>THOUGHT PROCESS — DECISION ENGINE</h2>
      <div class="cycle-phases" id="cycle-phases">
        <!-- Phases rendered by JS -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==============================
         CENTER: AGI BRAIN VISUALIZATION
         ============================== -->
    <div class="panel panel-brain">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot"></span>AGI NEURAL TOPOLOGY</h2>
      <svg id="brain-svg"></svg>
      <!-- Confidence gauge overlaid -->
      <div class="gauge-container">
        <svg class="gauge-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="gaugeGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#7c4dff"/>
              <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#00e5ff"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#00e676"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <circle class="gauge-bg" cx="50" cy="50" r="45"/>
          <circle class="gauge-fill" id="gauge-fill" cx="50" cy="50" r="45"/>
          <text class="gauge-value" id="gauge-value" x="50" y="46">0%</text>
          <text class="gauge-label" x="50" y="62">CONFIDENCE</text>
          <circle class="gauge-dot" id="gauge-dot" cx="50" cy="5" r="3" opacity="0"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==============================
         RIGHT TOP: DATA VISUALIZATIONS
         ============================== -->
    <div class="panel panel-charts">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-amber"></span>DATA VISUALIZATIONS</h2>
      <div class="charts-grid">
        <div class="mini-chart">
          <div class="mini-chart-title">Hypothesis Funnel</div>
          <canvas id="chart-funnel" aria-label="Hypothesis funnel chart"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-chart">
          <div class="mini-chart-title">Domain Activity</div>
          <canvas id="chart-domain" aria-label="Domain distribution chart"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-chart">
          <div class="mini-chart-title">Confidence Radar</div>
          <canvas id="chart-radar" aria-label="Capability radar chart"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-chart">
          <div class="mini-chart-title">H₀ Distribution</div>
          <canvas id="chart-h0" aria-label="Hubble constant chart"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-chart">
          <div class="mini-chart-title">Discovery Rate</div>
          <canvas id="chart-discovery" aria-label="Discovery timeline chart"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-chart">
          <div class="mini-chart-title">Error Rate</div>
          <canvas id="chart-error" aria-label="Error distribution chart"></canvas>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==============================
         RIGHT BOTTOM: DECISION LOG
         ============================== -->
    <div class="panel panel-decisions">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-emerald"></span>AUTONOMOUS DECISION LOG</h2>
      <div class="decisions-list" id="decisions-list" role="log" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Decision log"></div>
    </div>

  </div><!-- /main-grid -->

  <!-- ==============================
       FULL-WIDTH: METRICS BAR
       ============================== -->
  <div class="metrics-row">
    <div class="panel">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-amber"></span>SYSTEM METRICS</h2>
      <div class="metrics-grid" id="metrics-grid"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div><!-- /tab-overview -->

<!-- ==================== TAB: SAFETY ==================== -->
<div class="tab-content" id="tab-safety" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-btn-safety">
  <div class="safety-grid">

    <!-- State Space Navigator -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-cyan"></span>STATE SPACE — MIND TRAJECTORY</h2>
      <svg class="state-space-svg" id="state-space-svg"></svg>
      <div class="layout-flex-between">
        <span>PC1: Confidence Variance</span>
        <span id="state-space-info">Basin: Nominal — 50 cycles</span>
        <span>PC2: Domain Diversity</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Anomaly & Drift Monitor -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in-d1">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-amber"></span>ANOMALY DETECTION — DRIFT MONITOR <span id="anomaly-count-badge" class="si-badge-amber">0</span></h2>
      <div id="anomaly-gauges"></div>
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8-bt">
        <div class="si-mono-label mb-6">RECENT ALERTS</div>
        <div class="alert-stream" id="alert-stream">
          <div class="empty-state si-p16">No anomalies detected</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Alignment Stability Dashboard -->
    <div class="panel panel-full si-fade-in-d2">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-emerald"></span>ALIGNMENT STABILITY</h2>
      <div class="layout-flex-wrap">
        <div class="layout-align-left">
          <span class="align-score-big" id="alignment-score">--</span>
          <span class="align-trend" id="alignment-trend">--%</span>
          <div class="si-mono-label mt-4">COMPOSITE ALIGNMENT</div>
        </div>
        <div class="layout-flex1" id="alignment-dimensions"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div><!-- /tab-safety -->

<!-- ==================== TAB: CONTROL ==================== -->
<div class="tab-content" id="tab-control" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-btn-control">
  <div class="control-grid">

    <!-- Emergency Intervention Console -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-coral"></span>INTERVENTION CONSOLE <span class="engine-state-badge" id="intervention-state">NOMINAL</span></h2>
      <div class="intervention-btns">
        <button class="intervention-btn btn-pause-big" onclick="safetyAction('pause')">⏸ PAUSE ENGINE</button>
        <button class="intervention-btn btn-stop-big" onclick="confirmEstop()">🛑 EMERGENCY STOP</button>
        <button class="intervention-btn btn-safe-big" onclick="safetyAction('safe-mode')">🛡 SAFE MODE</button>
        <button class="intervention-btn btn-resume-big" onclick="safetyAction('resume')">▶ RESUME</button>
      </div>
      <div class="si-mono-label m-8-0-4">QUICK ACTIONS</div>
      <div class="quick-actions">
        <button class="quick-action-btn" onclick="quickAction('rescan')" aria-label="Force data rescan">Force Rescan</button>
        <button class="quick-action-btn" onclick="quickAction('skip')" aria-label="Skip current hypothesis">Skip Hypothesis</button>
        <button class="quick-action-btn" onclick="quickAction('rollback')" aria-label="Rollback last cycle">Rollback Cycle</button>
        <button class="quick-action-btn" onclick="quickAction('export')" aria-label="Export system state">Export State</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Supervisor of Record -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in-d1">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-violet"></span>SUPERVISOR OF RECORD</h2>
      <div id="sor-panel-content">
        <div class="sor-panel-name" id="sor-name">No Supervisor Set</div>
        <div class="sor-panel-detail" id="sor-detail">Click "Sign In" to assume supervisory responsibility</div>
        <div class="layout-flex-gap8">
          <button class="quick-action-btn" onclick="sorSignIn()" id="sor-signin-btn" aria-label="Sign in as supervisor">Sign In as Supervisor</button>
          <button class="quick-action-btn" onclick="sorLogObservation()" aria-label="Log observation" style="display:none" id="sor-log-btn">Log Observation</button>
          <button class="quick-action-btn" onclick="sorHandoff()" aria-label="Initiate handoff" style="display:none" id="sor-handoff-btn">Initiate Handoff</button>
        </div>
        <div class="sor-actions-log" id="sor-actions-log"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pending Approvals -->
    <div class="panel panel-full si-fade-in-d2">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-emerald"></span>PENDING APPROVALS <span id="pending-count" class="si-badge-emerald">0</span></h2>
      <div id="pending-list">
        <div class="empty-state">No pending approvals — all clear ✓</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div><!-- /tab-control -->

<!-- ==================== TAB: HEALTH ==================== -->
<div class="tab-content" id="tab-health" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-btn-health">
  <div class="health-grid">

    <!-- Component Health Cards -->
    <div class="panel panel-full si-fade-in">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-emerald"></span>COMPONENT HEALTH <span id="health-pct" class="si-badge-emerald bg-none">--% UP</span></h2>
      <div class="health-components-grid" id="health-components"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Resource Charts -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in-d1">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-amber"></span>CYCLE PERFORMANCE</h2>
      <div class="chart-container" style="position:relative;height:180px;"><canvas id="chart-cycle-time" aria-label="Cycle time chart"></canvas></div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel si-fade-in-d15">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-cyan"></span>DOMAIN DISTRIBUTION</h2>
      <div class="chart-container" style="position:relative;height:180px;"><canvas id="chart-domain-health" aria-label="Domain health chart"></canvas></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Persistence (SQLite) -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in-d2">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-violet"></span>PERSISTENCE (SQLite)</h2>
      <div class="persistence-card" id="persistence-stats">
        <div class="persistence-stat">
          <div class="stat-value" id="persist-discoveries">--</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Discoveries</div>
        </div>
        <div class="persistence-stat">
          <div class="stat-value" id="persist-outcomes">--</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Outcomes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="persistence-stat">
          <div class="stat-value" id="persist-hypotheses">--</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Hypotheses</div>
        </div>
        <div class="persistence-stat">
          <div class="stat-value" id="persist-dbsize">--</div>
          <div class="stat-label">DB Size</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Audit Trail -->
    <div class="panel panel-full si-fade-in-d2">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-muted"></span>AUDIT TRAIL</h2>
      <div class="audit-log" id="audit-log"></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div><!-- /tab-health -->

<!-- ==================== TAB: PHASE 4 (Operational Readiness) ==================== -->
<div class="tab-content" id="tab-phase4" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-btn-phase4">
  <div class="health-grid">

    <!-- ORP Readiness -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-violet"></span>OPERATIONAL READINESS</h2>
      <div id="orp-readiness" class="si-p12">
        <div class="layout-flex-center-gap">
          <div id="orp-gonogo" class="orp-gonogo">--</div>
          <div id="orp-pct" class="si-info-mono-secondary">--% ready</div>
        </div>
        <div id="orp-checklist-summary" class="orp-checklist-info"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Safety Arbiter -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in-d1">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-cyan"></span>SAFETY ARBITER</h2>
      <div id="arbiter-panel" class="si-p12">
        <div class="phase4-claims-grid mb-12">
          <div class="si-stat-cell">
            <div class="si-mono-label-sm">GO Threshold</div>
            <div id="arbiter-go" class="si-mono-value-lg si-c-emerald">--</div>
          </div>
          <div class="si-stat-cell">
            <div class="si-mono-label-sm">NO-GO Threshold</div>
            <div id="arbiter-nogo" class="si-mono-value-lg si-c-coral">--</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="arbiter-verdicts" class="si-scroll-sm"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Safety Case / Risk -->
    <div class="panel si-fade-in-d15">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-emerald"></span>SAFETY CASE</h2>
      <div id="safety-case-panel" class="si-p12">
        <div class="phase4-safety-grid mb-10">
          <div class="si-stat-cell-sm">
            <div class="si-mono-label-xs">HAZARDS</div>
            <div id="sc-hazards" class="si-mono-value si-c-amber">--</div>
          </div>
          <div class="si-stat-cell-sm">
            <div class="si-mono-label-xs">CLAIMS</div>
            <div id="sc-claims" class="si-mono-value si-c-cyan">--</div>
          </div>
          <div class="si-stat-cell-sm">
            <div class="si-mono-label-xs">RESIDUAL RISK</div>
            <div id="sc-risk" class="si-mono-value si-c-emerald">--</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="sc-hazard-list" class="si-scroll-md"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Supervisor & Ceremony -->
    <div class="panel panel-full si-fade-in-d2">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-amber"></span>SUPERVISOR & CEREMONY</h2>
      <div class="phase4-claims-grid p4-claims-gap">
        <div>
          <div class="si-info-label-upper">Active Supervisor</div>
          <div id="supervisor-name" class="si-info-mono-amber">--</div>
          <div id="supervisor-shift" class="si-info-sub mt-4"></div>
          <div id="supervisor-actions" class="si-info-sub mt-8"></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="si-info-label-upper">Ceremony Status</div>
          <div id="ceremony-state" class="si-info-mono-violet">No active ceremony</div>
          <div id="ceremony-details" class="si-info-sub mt-4"></div>
          <div id="ceremony-history" class="si-info-sub mt-8"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Rollback Procedures -->
    <div class="panel panel-full si-fade-in-d25">
      <h2 class="panel-title"><span class="dot dot-coral"></span>ROLLBACK PROCEDURES</h2>
      <div id="rollback-procedures" class="rollback-grid">
        <div class="si-stat-cell">
          <div class="si-rollback-label color-coral">FULL → CONDITIONAL</div>
          <div class="si-rollback-time">~5 min rollback</div>
        </div>
        <div class="si-stat-cell">
          <div class="si-rollback-label color-amber">CONDITIONAL → SUPERVISED</div>
          <div class="si-rollback-time">~3 min rollback</div>
        </div>
        <div class="si-stat-cell">
          <div class="si-rollback-label color-cyan">SUPERVISED → SHADOW</div>
          <div class="si-rollback-time">~1 min rollback</div>
        </div>
        <div class="si-stat-cell">
          <div class="si-rollback-label color-emerald">SHADOW → STOPPED</div>
          <div class="si-rollback-time">~30 sec rollback</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div><!-- /tab-phase4 -->

<!-- ==================== TAB: DISCOVERIES ==================== -->
<div class="tab-content" id="tab-discoveries" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-btn-discoveries">

  <!-- Dynamic Hypothesis Pipeline -->
  <div class="hyp-pipeline" id="hyp-pipeline-container">
    <div class="hyp-pipeline-header">⬡ Hypothesis Pipeline</div>
    <div id="hyp-pipeline-content"><p style="color:var(--text-tertiary);font-size:0.8rem;">Loading hypothesis data…</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="hyp-pipeline-header" style="margin-top:8px;">✦ Verified Discoveries</div>

  <div class="discoveries-grid">

    <!-- Kepler's Third Law -->
    <div class="panel si-discovery-full-cyan">
      <div class="panel-header">
        <span class="panel-icon">⚛</span>
        <span class="panel-title">KEPLER'S THIRD LAW — VERIFIED FROM 2,839 EXOPLANETS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discovery-body">
        <div class="discovery-detail-box discovery-box-cyan">
          Theory: P² ∝ a³/M* → log(P) = <strong>1.500</strong>·log(a) − <strong>0.500</strong>·log(M*) + C<br>
          ASTRA: log(P) = <strong>1.497</strong>·log(a) − <strong>0.474</strong>·log(M*) + C &nbsp;|&nbsp; R² = <strong>0.9982</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="discovery-desc">
          ASTRA independently recovered Newton's gravitational law from the NASA Exoplanet Archive. The semi-major axis exponent matches theory to <strong class="color-emerald">0.2%</strong> accuracy. This is one of the most precise empirical verifications of Kepler's Third Law from exoplanet data — measured blindly by a discovery system with zero prior assumptions about orbital mechanics.
        </div>
        <div class="discovery-meta">
          <span>📡 NASA Exoplanet Archive (TAP)</span>
          <span>🔢 2,839 confirmed exoplanets</span>
          <span>📊 Pearson r = 0.9945</span>
          <span class="discovery-stat-badge badge-fdr">FDR corrected</span>
          <span class="discovery-stat-badge badge-effect">d = 1.42 (large)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Accelerating Universe -->
    <div class="panel si-discovery-full-amber">
      <div class="panel-header">
        <span class="panel-icon">🌌</span>
        <span class="panel-title">THE ACCELERATING UNIVERSE — MEASURED FROM 1,701 SUPERNOVAE</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discovery-body">
        <div class="discovery-detail-box discovery-box-amber">
          Hubble diagram: μ = <strong>5.33</strong>·log(z) + 24.42 &nbsp;|&nbsp; r = <strong>0.9982</strong><br>
          Pure Hubble law predicts slope = 5.00 &nbsp;→&nbsp; ASTRA measured: <strong>5.33</strong> (+6.6% excess)
        </div>
        <div class="discovery-desc">
          The distance modulus slope being steeper than 5.0 means luminosity distance grows <em>faster</em> than a non-accelerating universe predicts. This is exactly the signature of dark energy / cosmological constant that won the <strong class="color-amber">2011 Nobel Prize</strong> (Perlmutter, Schmidt, Riess). ASTRA found it independently from the full Pantheon+ sample. Binned residuals show the deviation is strongest at z &gt; 0.5 — consistent with acceleration onset.
        </div>
        <div class="discovery-meta">
          <span>📡 Pantheon+ SH0ES (GitHub)</span>
          <span>🔢 1,701 Type Ia supernovae</span>
          <span>📊 χ²/dof = 0.64</span>
          <span class="discovery-stat-badge badge-fdr">BH α* = 0.016</span>
          <span class="discovery-stat-badge badge-effect">Laplace CI: ±0.83</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Galaxy Bimodality -->
    <div class="panel si-discovery-accent-coral">
      <div class="panel-header">
        <span class="panel-icon">🔴🔵</span>
        <span class="panel-title">GALAXY DEATH IN REAL TIME</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discovery-body">
        <div class="discovery-detail-box discovery-box-coral">
          <table class="discovery-table">
            <tr class="discovery-table-header"><th class="text-left">Redshift</th><th>u-g</th><th>Blue %</th></tr>
            <tr><td>z = 0.02–0.05</td><td class="text-center">1.44</td><td class="text-center color-blue">50%</td></tr>
            <tr><td>z = 0.05–0.10</td><td class="text-center">1.70</td><td class="text-center color-amber">23%</td></tr>
            <tr><td>z = 0.10–0.15</td><td class="text-center">1.77</td><td class="text-center color-coral">16%</td></tr>
            <tr><td>z = 0.15–0.25</td><td class="text-center">1.92</td><td class="text-center color-coral">10%</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="discovery-desc">
          From 2,000 SDSS galaxies: the blue fraction (actively star-forming) drops from 50% to 10% over the last 3 billion years. This is cosmic <strong class="color-coral">"downsizing"</strong> — star formation shuts off progressively. The bimodal color distribution (peaks at u-g ≈ 1.4 and 1.9) is the famous red sequence / blue cloud.
        </div>
        <div class="si-muted-note">
          �📡 SDSS DR18 · 🔢 2,000 galaxies · 📊 z–color r = 0.33
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- HR Diagram -->
    <div class="panel si-discovery-accent-violet">
      <div class="panel-header">
        <span class="panel-icon">⭐</span>
        <span class="panel-title">STELLAR PHYSICS FROM GAIA DR3</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discovery-body">
        <div class="discovery-detail-box discovery-box-violet">
          Main sequence: M_G = <strong>3.66</strong> × (BP-RP) &nbsp;|&nbsp; r = <strong>0.90</strong><br>
          MS slope ~2–3 expected · ASTRA: 3.66 (includes metallicity scatter)
        </div>
        <div class="discovery-desc">
          From 4,984 Gaia DR3 stars (parallax S/N &gt; 10). Density peaks at <strong class="color-violet">M_G ≈ 6.3</strong> (K-dwarf main sequence), <strong class="color-violet">12.5</strong> (white dwarfs), and <strong class="color-violet">1.8</strong> (subgiants). All three major stellar populations independently identified from raw astrometry.
        </div>
        <div class="si-muted-note">
          📡 Gaia DR3 TAP · 🔢 4,984 stars · BP-RP ∈ [−0.5, 3.2]
        </div>
      </div>
